import React from "react";
import {
  ButtonContainer,
  Container,
  Form,
  Inner,
  InputContainer,
  UserImg,
  UserInfo,
  UserText,
  UserTextBox,
  Wrap,
} from "./styled";
import {
  Button,
  ContentContainer,
  Hr,
  Input,
  Label,
  Title,
} from "src/commonStyles";
import { SubmitHandler, useForm } from "react-hook-form";
import CompanyCard from "../Companies/CompanyCard/CompanyCard";

interface IFormInput {
  firstName: string;
  lastName: string;
  birthday: string;
  sex: string;
  country: string;
  city: string;
  login: string;
  email: string;
}

export default function PersonalCabinet() {
  const {
    register,
    handleSubmit,
    formState: { errors },
    reset,
  } = useForm<IFormInput>();

  const onSubmit: SubmitHandler<IFormInput> = (data) => {
    console.log(data);
    reset();
  };

  return (
    <Wrap>
      <ContentContainer>
        <Title>Личный кабинет</Title>
        <Hr />
        <Inner>
          <UserInfo>
            <UserImg $backgroundImg="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1633332755192-727a05c4013d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8Mnx8dXNlcnxlbnwwfHwwfHx8MA%3D%3D&w=1000&q=80" />
            <UserTextBox>
              <UserText>Иванов Иван</UserText>
              <UserText>id:123</UserText>
            </UserTextBox>
          </UserInfo>
          <Form>
            <Container>
              <InputContainer>
                <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                  Имя
                </Label>
                <Input id="" $width="349px" />
              </InputContainer>
              <InputContainer>
                <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                  Фамилия
                </Label>
                <Input id="" $width="349px" />
              </InputContainer>
            </Container>
            <Container>
              <InputContainer>
                <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                  Дата рождения
                </Label>
                <Input id="" $width="349px" />
              </InputContainer>
              <InputContainer>
                <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                  Пол
                </Label>
                <Input id="" $width="349px" />
              </InputContainer>
            </Container>
            <Container>
              <InputContainer>
                <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                  Страна
                </Label>
                <Input id="" $width="349px" />
              </InputContainer>
              <InputContainer>
                <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                  Город
                </Label>
                <Input id="" $width="349px" />
              </InputContainer>
            </Container>
            <Container>
              <InputContainer>
                <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                  Логин
                </Label>
                <Input id="" $width="753px" />
              </InputContainer>
            </Container>
            <Container>
              <InputContainer>
                <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                  E-mail
                </Label>
                <Input id="" $width="753px" />
              </InputContainer>
            </Container>
            <ButtonContainer>
              <Button $gray>Сменить пароль</Button>
            </ButtonContainer>
            <ButtonContainer>
              <Button type="submit">Сохранить</Button>
            </ButtonContainer>
          </Form>
        </Inner>
        <Title>Ваши компании:</Title>
        <Wrap>
          <Container>
            <CompanyCard
              key={1}
              imgUrl={
                "http://localhost:3000/static/media/company-img.3ee103e2549bf8865a2c.png"
              }
              name={""}
              reviewsScore={4}
            />
          </Container>
          {/* {cards.length === 0 && <Container>Нет компаний</Container>} */}
        </Wrap>
      </ContentContainer>
    </Wrap>
  );
}
